          "reviewBody": "Sri chaitanya Madurawada -2 is one of the worst school. No ethics with zero values. Mainly for Principal he will not stand on his words. while getting admission he will commit for something and after admission he will kick you out simply. so be careful because you can not shift your kid in middle of academic.\n\nIn my case same thing happened and now he told if you are not able to drop your kid then simply leave the school..(After paying school bus fees.. that too double of the regular fee.) when we went for admission he said their bus will pick our kid at my society since one kid already usingtheir bus at same location and after admission he said that we never collected kids from my society. (Simply lying... if school principal it self lying then what their school teaching to children? )\n\nPreviously only one kid used to go from my society and bus used to pic her daily infront of society and now 3 kids and asking us to collect them from high way... who will responsible for kids if he drops children at highway? why we have opted for school bus?",
